defs/js/plus.plus_.property.accelerometer.description: The accelerator module manages the acceleration sensor of the device, which is used to obtain the acceleration information of the device, including the acceleration information of X (horizontal direction of the screen), y (horizontal direction of the vertical screen) and Z (plane direction of the vertical screen). adopt plus.accelerometer Get the device acceleration sensor management object.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.ad.description: The ad module realizes the uni ad advertising alliance function, aggregates the popular domestic advertising platforms, such as Tencent, pangolin, 360 advertising, and supports information flow, banner and other advertising.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.android.description: Native.js  For Android encapsulates a way to call native java interface directly through JS syntax plus.android It can call almost all system APIs.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.audio.description: The audio module is used to provide audio recording and playback functions. It can call the microphone device of the system for recording operation, and also call the speaker device of the system to play audio files. adopt plus.audio Gets the audio management object.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.barcode.description: Barcode module manages barcode (one-dimensional code and two-dimensional code) scanning and recognition, supports common one-dimensional code (such as EAN13 code) and two-dimensional code (such as QR code). By calling the camera of the device to scan and identify the barcode, decode the barcode and return the code data content and code type.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.bluetooth.description: Bluetooth module is used to manage Bluetooth devices, search nearby Bluetooth devices and realize simple data transmission.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.camera.description: The camera module manages the camera of the device, which can be used to take pictures and take pictures plus.camera Get the camera management object.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.contacts.description: The contacts module manages the address book of the system, which is used to add, delete, modify and check the address book of the system. adopt plus.contacts Get the system address book management object.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.device.description: The device module manages the device information, which is used to obtain the relevant information of mobile devices, such as IMEI, IMSI, model, manufacturer, etc. adopt plus.device Get the device information management object.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.display.description: The display module manages the display area information that can be used by the application
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.downloader.description: The downloader module manages the network file download task, which is used to download various files from the server, and supports cross domain access operation. adopt plus.downloader Get the download management object. Downloader download uses HTTP get / post to request the download file, which conforms to the standard HTTP / HTTPS transport protocol.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.gallery.description: Gallery module manages the album of the system, supports the functions of selecting pictures or video files from the album, saving pictures or video files to the album, etc. adopt plus.gallery Gets the album management object.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.geolocation.description: The geolocation module manages the location information of the device, which is used to obtain the geographic location information, such as longitude, latitude and so on. adopt plus.geolocation Get the device location management object. Although W3C has provided standard API to obtain location information, there are differences or not implemented in some platforms. In order to maintain the unity of various platforms, this specification interface is defined to obtain location information.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.ibeacon.description: The ibeacon module is used to search ibeacon devices for attachments.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.io.description: IO module manages the local file system, which is used to browse the directory of the file system, read and write files. adopt plus.io Gets the file system management object.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.ios.description: Native.js  For IOS encapsulates an interface channel that directly calls native Objective-C through JS syntax plus.ios It can call almost all system APIs.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.maps.description: The maps module manages the map control, which is used to display the map control in the web page, and provides various interfaces to operate the map control, such as adding punctuation, route and so on. adopt plus.maps Map management objects can be obtained.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.messaging.description: The messaging module manages the device communication function, which can be used for SMS, MMS, e-mail sending, etc. adopt plus.messaging Can get the device communication management object. In addition, you can also send short messages, make phone calls and send e-mails directly and quickly through the HTML.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.nativeObj.description: Native obj management system native object.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.nativeUI.description: Native UI management system native interface can be used to pop up the system native prompt dialog box window, time and date selection dialog box, waiting dialog box, etc.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.navigator.description: Navigator is used to manage the running environment information of browser
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.net.description: The XMLHttpRequest module manages network requests, which is consistent with the use of XMLHttpRequest in standard HTML. The difference is that the former can carry out cross domain access. adopt plus.net Get the network request management object.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.networkinfo.description: The networkinfo module is used to obtain network information
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.oauth.description: OAuth module manages the user login authentication function of the client, and allows the application to access the resources of the third-party platform.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.orientation.description: The orientation module manages the direction information of the device, including alpha, beta and gamma plus.orientation The device direction management object can be obtained.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.os.description: OS module manages operating system information
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.payment.description: The payment module manages the payment function, which is used to provide web page security payment ability and support payment operation through web interface. adopt plus.payment Access to payment management objects.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.proximity.description: The proximity module manages the distance sensor of the device, which can obtain the proximity information of the current device plus.proximity The device distance sensing management object can be obtained.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.push.description: Push module management push message function, can achieve online, offline message push, through the plus.push The push message management object can be obtained.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.runtime.description: The runtime module manages the running environment, which can be used to obtain the current running environment information and communicate with other programs. adopt plus.runtime Gets the runtime environment management object.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.screen.description: Screen module manages device screen information
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.share.description: The share module manages the social sharing function of the client and provides the sharing ability to call the terminal social software. adopt plus.share Access to social sharing management objects.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.speech.description: Speech module manages speech input function, provides speech recognition function, and supports users to input speech content through microphone device. adopt plus.speech The voice input management object can be obtained.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.sqlite.description: SQLite module is used to operate local database files, which can create database files and execute SQL statements.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.statistic.description: Statistics module is used to manage statistics function, which is used to provide the ability of statistics within the application, and support the statistics and analysis of user attributes and user behavior data. adopt plus.statistic The statistics management object can be obtained.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.storage.description: The storage module manages the application local data storage area, which is used to save and read the application data. The difference between application local data and local storage and session storage is that the data valid domain is different. The former can operate across domains within the application, and the data storage period is persistent, and there is no capacity limit. adopt plus.storage The local data management object of the application can be obtained.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.stream.description: The stream module operates the stream application.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.uploader.description: Uploader module manages the network upload task, which is used to upload various files from local to server, and supports cross domain access operation. adopt plus.uploader The upload management object can be obtained. Uploader uploads and submits data in HTTP post mode. The data format conforms to multipart / form data specification, namely rfc1867 (form based file upload in HTML) protocol.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.video.description: The video module can manage multimedia video related capabilities, such as creating video playback controls, live streaming controls, etc.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.webview.description: The WebView module manages the application window interface and realizes the logical control and management operation of multiple windows. adopt plus.webview The application interface management object can be obtained.
defs/js/plus.plus_.property.zip.description: Zip module manages the compression and decompression of files plus.zip Gets the compressed management object.
